response.overview: March 11th, 2017 :: American Combat Wrestling presents Luck Of The Irish 2017 from Port Richey, Florida, USA. Matches include: • Jon Cruz vs. Nick Nero vs. Richard Delicious vs. Jayson Falcone vs. Snoop Strikes vs. Hunter Law • Rhett Giddins (w/Bombay Brown, Josh Hess & Stormie Lee) vs. Danhausen • CJ O'Doyle (Bombay Brown, Josh Hess, Rhett Giddins & Stormie Lee) vs. Mitch Mitchell • Candy Cartwright (w/Aria Blake) vs. Kaci Lennox • ACW Combat Title Match Romeo Quevedo (c) vs. Omar Amir (w/Chance Champion & Skinny Vinny) • Irish Jack & Mila Naniki vs. Aspyn Rose & Bryan Idol • ACW Tag Team Title Match The Lacey Twins (Gabe Lacey & Greyson Lacey) (c) vs. The Dirty Blondes (Leo Brien & Mike Patrick) • FIP Florida Heritage Title Match Martin Stone (c) vs. Chance Champion (w/Skinny Vinny) • Stateline (Damien Angel & Eddie Taurus) & David Mercury vs. The Hierarchy (Adrian Armour, Chip Day & Murder-1) • ACW Heavyweight Title Match Parrow (w/Drennan) (c) vs. Jason Cade.
response.title: ACW Luck Of The Irish 2017
